{"tid":469950,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人飲熱檸水會食埋d檸檬","createTime":"2017-11-15T23:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T04:33:27.000Z","uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46d9a8a3dd9b02e521b0f0ba17ea41a148f09dcf","tid":469950,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"我每日早餐都會咁做<br />\n感覺幾爽又健康<br />\n重點一粒糖都唔可架<br />\n而且唔可以空腹飲"},{"pid":"678da4c5daeee10e1dfaf1fdb7ef506a48a23e6b","tid":469950,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我每日早餐都會咁做<br />\n感覺幾爽又健康<br />\n重點一粒糖都唔可架<br />\n而且唔可以空腹飲</blockquote><br />\n點解唔可以空肚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bfe0154a7e4ca442cd448dc399a5e465ce5f67","tid":469950,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我每日早餐都會咁做<br />\n感覺幾爽又健康<br />\n重點一粒糖都唔可架<br />\n而且唔可以空腹飲</blockquote><br />\n點解唔可以空肚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n空腹時若喝檸檬水等偏酸飲品，恐大量刺激胃酸分泌，長期下來易增加胃食道逆流，甚至造成食道和胃的交界處灼傷，而出現火燒心症狀，這會引起巴瑞特氏食道，罹患食道癌的風險也將大增，因此不建議這種喝法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom apple"},{"pid":"8bf1a17c972ee3189bd35d9d0b89ed32010d91e1","tid":469950,"uid":34394,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:50:27.000Z","msg":"啲檸檬又污糟又唔知膒咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94da4b90bcdbe7589e1972b7386d3a4d4817998f","tid":469950,"uid":192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲檸檬又污糟又唔知膒咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我建議你唔好出街食<br />\n好危險"},{"pid":"8424a86433e8ce74273de9146f040066434c882a","tid":469950,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲檸檬又污糟又唔知膒咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲自己種"},{"pid":"757f8fd50e9446913b9a5e54f34e9ab417d3978d","tid":469950,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲檸檬又污糟又唔知膒咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲自己種</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa6a981e660baab1cfa2fea21a4dbd058d7cb56","tid":469950,"uid":44031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:21:41.000Z","msg":"我唔會食埋啲檸檬 但係會食埋隻杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7e539726dd5d8dbff4589ac9541ceb506e1271","tid":469950,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:36:18.000Z","msg":"我食食埋飲筒<br />\n費事比環保撚屌污染海洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9205bcfc1192208ce35a3d751744565b68ab84c","tid":469950,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我食食埋飲筒<br />\n費事比環保撚屌污染海洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱檸水用飲筒咁高難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}